WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.834
Why I keep watching you?

2
00:00:00.834 --> 00:00:05.005
Could I be in love with you?

3
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:13.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

4
00:00:20.604 --> 00:00:21.772
Hey...

5
00:00:21.772 --> 00:00:23.815
... how did you get here?

6
00:00:23.899 --> 00:00:26.860
Namtarn.
can I take a picture with you?

7
00:00:28.904 --> 00:00:32.032
One... two... three...

8
00:00:33.075 --> 00:00:35.202
Thank you.

9
00:00:41.416 --> 00:00:43.544
Want to take a picture?

10
00:01:14.783 --> 00:01:16.910
Can you hold my baton?

11
00:01:16.910 --> 00:01:18.871
Okay. I'm ready.

12
00:01:18.871 --> 00:01:21.081
Big smile. okay?

13
00:01:21.957 --> 00:01:24.293
Your cheeks look like they're
going to burst.

14
00:01:24.293 --> 00:01:28.338
Okay... one... two... three...

15
00:01:42.895 --> 00:01:44.188
Hey. can I ask you something?

16
00:01:44.188 --> 00:01:46.148
Shoot.

17
00:01:49.234 --> 00:01:51.361
How did you die?

18
00:01:57.492 --> 00:01:59.745
I died of old age.

19
00:01:59.828 --> 00:02:02.956
Damn it... I'm serious.

20
00:02:06.001 --> 00:02:09.087
Wait a sec... I have to pee.

21
00:02:18.388 --> 00:02:20.474
Want to know...

22
00:02:20.516 --> 00:02:23.602
... why I got sent
here mid-term?

23
00:02:25.687 --> 00:02:27.856
Hey. it's already 6h PM.

24
00:02:27.856 --> 00:02:29.942
Let's hurry back.

25
00:02:55.050 --> 00:02:57.177
Vichien. wait up!

26
00:03:02.349 --> 00:03:07.604
Chatree Anantpitisuk.come meet
your parents in the dorm.

27
00:03:53.525 --> 00:03:57.446
Pen. follow me downstairs.

28
00:04:00.741 --> 00:04:04.745
Don't worry.
Everyone's asleep.

29
00:05:45.053 --> 00:05:47.097
Where have you been?

30
00:05:48.056 --> 00:05:49.183
What have you been up to?

31
00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:53.228
Why did you do this?
Tell me where you've been!

32
00:05:53.228 --> 00:05:54.479
Don't let me catch
you again!

33
00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:58.525
Did you hear me?
Don't do this ever again!

34
00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:03.572
... though we are apart...

35
00:06:03.614 --> 00:06:10.996
... I can still feel your heart...

36
00:06:10.996 --> 00:06:15.209
... in my embrace.

37
00:06:15.209 --> 00:06:23.342
We once loved each other...

38
00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:25.511
Chatree...

39
00:06:25.552 --> 00:06:27.804
... Miss Pranee asked me to
bring this to you.

40
00:06:34.895 --> 00:06:38.065
Here...
your dad sent this for you.

41
00:06:56.959 --> 00:07:00.087
Hey. where'd you go?
Your dad was here.

42
00:07:06.218 --> 00:07:08.470
Yeah? Well.
where did you disappear to?

43
00:07:12.474 --> 00:07:15.644
You said no one
cares about you.

44
00:07:15.644 --> 00:07:16.728
How about yourself?

45
00:07:16.728 --> 00:07:19.690
Do you care about anyone
else but yourself?

46
00:07:52.014 --> 00:07:55.350
If you've got something good.
you should share it with us.

47
00:07:56.351 --> 00:07:58.395
Why do I have to share it?

48
00:07:58.395 --> 00:08:02.566
Come on...
because we're buddies.

49
00:08:02.566 --> 00:08:05.652
Friends always share
with friends. right?

50
00:08:06.653 --> 00:08:09.740
Let's be friends. okay?

51
00:08:26.590 --> 00:08:29.801
I bet the new boy's a faggot.

52
00:08:29.843 --> 00:08:31.803
Why?

53
00:08:34.890 --> 00:08:37.059
I dunno. He seems like a fairy.

54
00:08:37.184 --> 00:08:41.188
I bet he reads gay porn.

55
00:08:41.230 --> 00:08:43.273
That's why he won't share.

56
00:08:43.273 --> 00:08:46.443
No wonder Miss Pranee
let him off lightly.

57
00:08:46.485 --> 00:08:49.404
And kept the porn
for herself.

58
00:08:49.404 --> 00:08:50.697
Pok.
lend me your sima lotion.

59
00:08:50.739 --> 00:08:53.575
I'm getting a rash again.

60
00:08:57.746 --> 00:08:58.830
Here you go.

61
00:08:59.873 --> 00:09:03.001
Damn! Do you have balls
like a dinosaur?

62
00:09:03.001 --> 00:09:04.211
How come it's all gone?

63
00:09:05.087 --> 00:09:07.130
Nui. do you have any?

64
00:09:09.424 --> 00:09:12.344
No. but I have formalin.
Want some?

65
00:09:12.344 --> 00:09:14.513
Save it for your dad!

66
00:09:19.810 --> 00:09:21.770
Want it?

67
00:09:24.857 --> 00:09:26.900
Err... thanks.

68
00:09:30.028 --> 00:09:31.280
Hold on.

69
00:09:32.239 --> 00:09:34.324
Do you have
any sima lotion?

70
00:09:42.583 --> 00:09:47.796
Pol.Capt. Vichai Chumchong
Sentenced to Prison for Corruption

71
00:09:49.798 --> 00:09:55.262
His Family Pleads for Mercy
from the Judge

72
00:10:04.479 --> 00:10:08.817
Pol.Capt. Vichai Chumchong
sentenced to 25 years in prison..

73
00:10:09.651 --> 00:10:11.987
Chatree. your mom's on the phone.

74
00:10:22.414 --> 00:10:24.291
Mom?

75
00:10:24.333 --> 00:10:26.418
Ton. it's your father.

76
00:10:27.336 --> 00:10:28.504
Umm... Ton...

77
00:10:30.506 --> 00:10:32.633
I asked Pen to move out of
our house. okay?

78
00:10:36.970 --> 00:10:40.974
How come you never pick up
the phone when I call?

79
00:10:52.486 --> 00:10:56.698
If you think that I sent you
away because of Pen...

80
00:10:56.782 --> 00:10:58.825
... then you're wrong.

81
00:11:02.788 --> 00:11:07.251
Umm... how do you like
your new school?

82
00:15:35.060 --> 00:15:39.106
Vichien.

83
00:16:15.726 --> 00:16:18.687
You have to stay
here every night...

84
00:16:19.897 --> 00:16:22.858
... because I'm sleeping
in your bed. right?

85
00:16:44.963 --> 00:16:46.089
Did he faint?

86
00:16:46.131 --> 00:16:50.093
No. I think he sniffed the ether
used to knock out the rabbits.

87
00:16:51.220 --> 00:16:55.224
Don't crowd him. Back off. boys.

88
00:16:56.308 --> 00:17:00.479
Chalemphol. how many times have
I told you not to sniff ether?

89
00:17:00.687 --> 00:17:02.689
He's regaining consciousness.

90
00:17:02.689 --> 00:17:04.858
He's not dead. He's not dead.

91
00:17:05.859 --> 00:17:07.736
It's like I died and
came back to life.

92
00:17:07.778 --> 00:17:10.072
Liar. You were only out
for a few seconds.

93
00:17:10.072 --> 00:17:14.159
But I really felt like I died.

94
00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:18.372
And I had trouble breathing.

95
00:17:18.413 --> 00:17:21.291
And everything was dark.

96
00:17:21.291 --> 00:17:22.543
And I saw...

97
00:17:22.584 --> 00:17:25.587
Wow. I can't believe it!

98
00:17:26.755 --> 00:17:28.757
If anyone wants to know...

99
00:17:29.591 --> 00:17:31.844
... what lies beyond death...

100
00:17:31.885 --> 00:17:33.929
... feel free to consult me.

101
00:17:34.012 --> 00:17:37.099
Hey fatso.. no one gives a shit
where your spirit went!

102
00:17:37.099 --> 00:17:39.059
I'm getting hungry.
Let's go.

103
00:18:32.404 --> 00:18:34.281
What the...!

104
00:19:21.328 --> 00:19:23.455
Vichien! Don't jump!

105
00:20:58.175 --> 00:21:00.302
Now you know...

106
00:21:01.512 --> 00:21:04.473
... how I died. right?

107
00:21:09.770 --> 00:21:11.939
Why did you drown yourself?

108
00:21:14.858 --> 00:21:17.861
Who said I drowned myself?

109
00:21:19.154 --> 00:21:22.115
It's more stupid than that.

110
00:21:24.409 --> 00:21:26.370
That day...

111
00:21:27.329 --> 00:21:29.331
... we didn't want
to stop swimming.

112
00:21:30.499 --> 00:21:32.751
It was getting dark.

113
00:21:37.881 --> 00:21:39.842
Help!

114
00:21:40.008 --> 00:21:42.052
Help me!

115
00:21:43.011 --> 00:21:45.264
Hey! Tira is drowning!
Tira is drowning!

116
00:21:57.776 --> 00:21:59.903
Where is he?

117
00:22:01.864 --> 00:22:03.991
Idiots! I fooled you!

118
00:22:03.991 --> 00:22:06.994
You were faking it?
That's pretty funny.

119
00:22:23.719 --> 00:22:24.970
Did you do your
homework yet?

120
00:22:25.012 --> 00:22:27.890
I forgot. It's for the
first period too.

121
00:22:32.060 --> 00:22:33.353
Help me!

122
00:22:34.229 --> 00:22:36.356
Hey... Vichien is drowning.

123
00:22:36.356 --> 00:22:38.400
Help me!

124
00:22:40.652 --> 00:22:43.530
Go ahead and save him.

125
00:22:43.530 --> 00:22:45.574
But he could be faking it.

126
00:22:47.910 --> 00:22:50.037
Help me!

127
00:23:04.384 --> 00:23:05.677
Help me!

128
00:23:22.277 --> 00:23:25.197
Hey. let's go. It's getting late.

129
00:23:25.197 --> 00:23:27.241
Let's go.

130
00:23:30.452 --> 00:23:32.496
Hey. I'm leaving now.

131
00:23:52.391 --> 00:23:55.686
Then how come
they say that...

132
00:23:55.686 --> 00:23:58.814
... Miss Pranee was related
to your death?

133
00:24:02.943 --> 00:24:05.946
Did you read that
newspaper?

134
00:24:13.245 --> 00:24:15.414
It's about my father.

135
00:24:15.497 --> 00:24:18.542
Miss Pranee didn't want
me to find out.

136
00:24:22.838 --> 00:24:24.673
Vichien!

137
00:24:25.674 --> 00:24:26.884
What are you doing?

138
00:24:27.843 --> 00:24:29.970
Who gave you
permission to enter?

139
00:24:29.970 --> 00:24:31.138
Come here.

140
00:24:31.847 --> 00:24:34.141
Why did you do this? Why?

141
00:24:35.184 --> 00:24:37.186
Why? I'll hit you until
I break your hand.

142
00:24:44.651 --> 00:24:47.779
I just wanted to read the
news about my father.

143
00:24:52.743 --> 00:24:56.121
Unfortunately.
Miss Pranee caught me first.

144
00:24:58.040 --> 00:25:01.168
Miss Pranee. Vichien hasn 't
returned to the dorm yet.

145
00:25:34.743 --> 00:25:37.788
Before my accident...

146
00:25:38.622 --> 00:25:41.875
... I managed to sneak back in
to steal the newspaper.

147
00:25:50.425 --> 00:25:52.386
Ever since then...

148
00:25:53.345 --> 00:25:57.474
... Miss Pranee has thought
that my death...

149
00:25:57.558 --> 00:25:59.726
... was her fault.

150
00:26:14.324 --> 00:26:17.286
But how come you
have to drown...

151
00:26:17.369 --> 00:26:19.496
... over and over like this?

152
00:26:21.456 --> 00:26:23.458
I don't know.

153
00:26:24.543 --> 00:26:28.672
Will you be stuck like this...
for much longer?

154
00:26:28.797 --> 00:26:30.924
I don't know myself.

155
00:26:31.925 --> 00:26:36.221
But it's really cold
at the bottom.

156
00:27:07.336 --> 00:27:10.506
See...didn't I tell you.

157
00:27:10.547 --> 00:27:14.676
That it must be the boy who
drowned in the pool?

158
00:27:15.844 --> 00:27:19.932
I've seen ghosts
like this before.

159
00:27:21.975 --> 00:27:24.144
At my old house...

160
00:27:24.186 --> 00:27:28.273
a motorcycle crashed rounding
the corner at night.

161
00:27:34.488 --> 00:27:38.534
The driver flew off his bike
and died instantly.

162
00:27:39.743 --> 00:27:41.703
After that night...

163
00:27:41.703 --> 00:27:44.831
... I'd hear the same motorbike...

164
00:27:44.831 --> 00:27:48.126
... skid around the corner
almost every night.

165
00:28:23.579 --> 00:28:27.749
As if the spirit hadn't
been reborn yet...

166
00:28:28.542 --> 00:28:31.753
so it had to re-enact it's death...

167
00:28:31.837 --> 00:28:35.883
... over and over.

168
00:28:53.734 --> 00:28:55.694
What then?

169
00:28:55.694 --> 00:28:57.905
We moved the heck out of there.

170
00:28:57.946 --> 00:28:59.823
No...

171
00:28:59.823 --> 00:29:01.116
How do we help the
spirits get reborn...

172
00:29:01.116 --> 00:29:03.202
... so they stop re-enacting
their own deaths?

173
00:29:04.077 --> 00:29:09.249
Ghosts and humans occupy
separate worlds.

174
00:29:09.291 --> 00:29:12.503
To help a ghost
you must be a ghost.

175
00:29:12.544 --> 00:29:15.631
To be a ghost.
you have to die first.

176
00:29:15.631 --> 00:29:20.761
Unless you can split your spirit
from your body.

177
00:30:28.412 --> 00:30:29.663
Are you crazy?

178
00:30:29.663 --> 00:30:32.666
Why would you want to die?

179
00:30:35.794 --> 00:30:37.004
Ton...

180
00:30:37.045 --> 00:30:39.882
... swear that you won't do it.

181
00:30:46.221 --> 00:30:48.390
Hey. promise me.

182
00:30:51.560 --> 00:30:54.563
Dr. Nui. what the hell
are you looking at?

183
00:30:55.564 --> 00:30:57.900
Something's wrong with Chatree.

184
00:30:57.900 --> 00:30:59.943
He seems strange.

185
00:31:00.027 --> 00:31:03.030
Shit. the other day you said
he wasn't strange.

186
00:31:03.030 --> 00:31:05.073
I know.

187
00:31:05.240 --> 00:31:09.369
But today he seems strange.

188
00:31:09.411 --> 00:31:11.288
Maybe...

189
00:31:11.288 --> 00:31:13.457
... he's going to
jump off the building.

190
00:31:14.291 --> 00:31:17.461
How the hell can he jump
through the grille?

191
00:31:25.844 --> 00:31:27.971
Can you see that water tank?

192
00:31:29.181 --> 00:31:32.184
I've climbed to the top before.

193
00:31:32.267 --> 00:31:34.394
The view is even nicer
than from up there.

194
00:31:37.523 --> 00:31:40.442
I'll take you there some day.

195
00:32:06.635 --> 00:32:09.763
Chatree has disappeared.

196
00:32:21.316 --> 00:32:23.443
Playing during dinner again?

197
00:32:23.443 --> 00:32:27.322
You'll see...
I'll teach you a lesson.

198
00:33:04.026 --> 00:33:06.069
Hey. Chatree! Chatree!

199
00:33:09.198 --> 00:33:10.240
Chatree. are you okay?

200
00:33:10.365 --> 00:33:13.160
Chatree. wake up!

201
00:33:18.498 --> 00:33:19.750
Killed himself. right?

202
00:33:20.709 --> 00:33:22.711
No.

203
00:33:22.711 --> 00:33:24.755
I think he split his spirit
from his body.

204
00:33:24.838 --> 00:33:25.881
What are you talking about?

205
00:33:25.881 --> 00:33:27.841
Splitting spirits from what?

206
00:33:27.883 --> 00:33:29.176
He told me himself...

207
00:33:29.927 --> 00:33:33.138
that he wanted to help his
friend that drowned in the pool.

208
00:33:33.305 --> 00:33:37.309
I suggested he could if he split
his spirit from his body.

209
00:33:48.946 --> 00:33:50.739
Trust me...

210
00:33:50.822 --> 00:33:52.866
... we have to take him
to the old pool.

211
00:33:54.201 --> 00:33:57.120
Miss Pranee.
Chatree killed himself.

212
00:34:32.656 --> 00:34:34.700
Vichien's drowning!

213
00:34:41.039 --> 00:34:42.916
Help me!

214
00:35:18.327 --> 00:35:19.536
Here!

215
00:35:19.578 --> 00:35:20.662
What's that for?

216
00:35:20.662 --> 00:35:23.624
You idiot! To break the lock!

217
00:35:41.350 --> 00:35:43.477
What do we do now?

218
00:35:57.199 --> 00:36:00.327
You told me that no
one cares about you.

219
00:36:00.327 --> 00:36:02.204
How about yourself?

220
00:36:02.204 --> 00:36:04.331
Do you care about anyone
else but yourself?

221
00:36:13.674 --> 00:36:16.677
Hey... let me go!

222
00:37:00.637 --> 00:37:02.598
Are you still mad
at your friends...

223
00:37:02.598 --> 00:37:04.808
... for not saving you from
drowning?

224
00:37:04.808 --> 00:37:06.810
No. I'm not mad anymore.

225
00:37:08.937 --> 00:37:10.105
How about you?

226
00:37:10.105 --> 00:37:12.107
Do you still want to run
away from school?

227
00:37:12.107 --> 00:37:14.109
No. not anymore.

228
00:37:14.151 --> 00:37:18.280
If I did. I would run straight
to Namtarn's embrace.

229
00:37:18.447 --> 00:37:21.325
Hey. hey...
I know what you're thinking.

230
00:37:21.366 --> 00:37:23.577
Don't! I remember the way
you looked at her. too.

231
00:37:23.619 --> 00:37:25.746
I've had my heart set
on her for years.

232
00:37:26.747 --> 00:37:28.916
When will we go visit
her again?

233
00:37:37.299 --> 00:37:39.301
Hey... Ton...

234
00:37:46.433 --> 00:37:48.477
... I've got to leave now.

235
00:38:51.206 --> 00:38:53.125
Hey... Chatree is coming to.

236
00:39:09.850 --> 00:39:11.894
Miss Pranee.
Chatree is fine now.

237
00:40:02.152 --> 00:40:05.322
I never knew our
school was this big.

238
00:40:06.114 --> 00:40:09.368
Hey... Why are you so amazed.
About the side of the school?

239
00:40:09.451 --> 00:40:11.286
I know from experience.

240
00:40:11.328 --> 00:40:13.580
Miss Pranee made me run
around the school before.

241
00:40:13.580 --> 00:40:15.624
Tears are falling from my eyes.

242
00:40:15.624 --> 00:40:18.710
You're the
one who's going to fall.

243
00:40:18.710 --> 00:40:20.921
Okay. calm down.

244
00:40:20.921 --> 00:40:23.799
I was only kidding.

245
00:40:25.843 --> 00:40:27.094
Hey. Ton...

246
00:40:28.011 --> 00:40:31.098
..why didn't you tell Miss Pranee
the truth about Vichien?

247
00:40:31.139 --> 00:40:35.227
Yeah. instead of letting us
all get punished.

248
00:40:38.438 --> 00:40:40.774
I don't think
she'd believe me.

249
00:40:41.733 --> 00:40:45.779
But... we all believe you.

250
00:40:45.946 --> 00:40:49.908
If you happen to
see another ghost...

251
00:40:49.992 --> 00:40:52.953
... feel free to consult me. okay?

252
00:40:53.036 --> 00:40:55.289
But don't consult me.
okay?

253
00:40:55.289 --> 00:40:58.500
Let me be the first one to
consult you then.

254
00:40:58.500 --> 00:41:01.545
Why the heck do you
speak with a lisp?

255
00:41:10.846 --> 00:41:15.976
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please
meet your parents in the dorm.

256
00:41:16.185 --> 00:41:22.107
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please
meet your parents in the dorm.

257
00:41:22.149 --> 00:41:24.401
I guess I'm off.

258
00:41:26.486 --> 00:41:28.530
See you guys next year.

259
00:41:30.782 --> 00:41:32.784
Good luck. man.

260
00:41:32.868 --> 00:41:34.870
Good luck.

261
00:41:48.300 --> 00:41:51.386
Ton. take me to see the
swimming pool. please!

262
00:41:51.386 --> 00:41:53.680
Be patient. Toh.
Let him pack his things first.

263
00:41:53.680 --> 00:41:55.641
Okay.
but then can we see it?

264
00:41:55.641 --> 00:41:56.808
Yes. dear.

265
00:42:01.855 --> 00:42:04.149
Having you been
eating enough food?

266
00:42:04.191 --> 00:42:07.194
You've gotten darker.

267
00:42:07.194 --> 00:42:09.154
And lost weight as well.

268
00:42:09.154 --> 00:42:11.365
You've been playing
outdoors too much. right?

269
00:42:14.493 --> 00:42:16.578
Mom. you're embarassing me.

270
00:42:16.620 --> 00:42:18.497
Why be embarassed?

271
00:42:18.539 --> 00:42:22.709
When you're older I won't
get to hug you anymore.

272
00:42:25.963 --> 00:42:29.007
Toh. stay around here. okay.

273
00:42:29.091 --> 00:42:31.218
Let's get your bags. dear.

274
00:42:53.282 --> 00:42:55.158
Dad...

275
00:42:57.244 --> 00:42:59.329
I like this school now.

276
00:43:32.779 --> 00:43:34.615
Miss Pranee...

277
00:43:41.997 --> 00:43:44.041
Vichien didn't kill himself.

278
00:43:47.377 --> 00:43:52.466
His drowning was
really an accident.

279
00:43:59.932 --> 00:44:02.893
Vichien asked me
to apologize...

280
00:44:03.852 --> 00:44:06.980
... for breaking your
record player that day.

281
00:44:14.446 --> 00:44:16.406
He knows that...

282
00:44:17.407 --> 00:44:19.660
... you were concerned about him.

283
00:44:28.043 --> 00:44:30.003
Thank you. Miss Pranee...

284
00:44:30.045 --> 00:44:32.172
... for always taking care of us.

285
00:44:34.132 --> 00:44:35.217
See you next year.
Miss Pranee.

286
00:45:20.053 --> 00:45:24.266
I still remember the first day
my father took me home.

287
00:45:26.435 --> 00:45:31.565
It was a Friday afternoon
much like any other.

288
00:45:31.607 --> 00:45:35.736
But something had
changed inside of me.

289
00:45:36.862 --> 00:45:39.990
That term. I only grew
two centimetres.

290
00:45:40.782 --> 00:45:43.118
It'll be a while before I'm
a grown man.

291
00:45:46.079 --> 00:45:50.292
Being friends with Vichien made
me see things more clearly.

292
00:46:07.142 --> 00:46:09.228
At that time.
I didn't know...

293
00:46:09.269 --> 00:46:14.149
... what adventures the
next term had in store.

294
00:46:14.316 --> 00:46:18.320
But I knew that I wanted to
rejoin my gang of friends.

295
00:46:18.403 --> 00:46:23.534
Because I've learned that with
one close friend by your side...

296
00:46:23.575 --> 00:46:26.662
... Even the worst things in life...

297
00:46:26.662 --> 00:46:29.915
... will eventually pass...

298
00:46:30.082 --> 00:46:33.001
... in just one short breath.

299
00:46:34.305 --> 00:47:34.218
Do you want subtitles for any video?
